title: Bird Hunter: Waterfowl Edition
description: Bird Hunter: Waterfowl Edition--All your favorite waterfowl are moving about in full-motion 3-D on land, in the air, and on the water. There are mallards, canvasback, pintail, green wings, and more. With changing weather, spectacular locations, and birds that react to both decoys and hunters, this adventure is so real you may want your rain gear.
